column52: Amber Heard has been an abusive bully for far too long. She's been able to get away with her crimes. This time she has come after Twitter users, trampling on their 1st Amendment Rights. We want her criminally charged for her legal attepts through her lawyer & the court to invade innocent people's privacy. Amber Heard is a celebrity. She made the choice to pubilcally broadcast her personal drama for the world when she went on various interviews to defame, slander and create her hoax against Johnny Depp. She invited the world into her life. Then she began taking large sums of money to speak on the subject. Amber Heard reacted in fury when her plan backfired & her lies were & still are being exposed. As a result she wishes to control how people discuss the drama she started. I'm asking that Twitter protect out privacy. Otherwise no one will trust the social media site. We want our rights upheld. Please criminally charge Amber Heard for Harassment & Violating our Rights!

column2:
Ms Heard claimed to have donated millions of her divorce settlement to two charities. Subsequent court proceedings indicate that years later they have not received any donations from her. Charities rely on people making good on their pledge so that they can help those that are less fortunate. She pledged $3.5m to each charity, a total of $7m.

- I will no longer support any charity or cause Ms Heard is an ambassador of. (Apologies to the charities but you will need to find more appropriate advocates or ambassadors).

- I will no longer buy or support any product Ms Heard is promoting, paid or otherwise. Including employment in any capacity she has in any aspect within the media, particularly the movie industry.

column2: This woman needs to be stopped she's done nothing by the book, she goes out of her way to antagonise genuine abuse victims and she doesn't let the law stand in her way of what she wants she will bend break it as many times as she sees fit to get her way and you can't be allowed to get away with that she needs to be taken down now!

column51: Federal Bureau of Investigation: Charge Amber Heard for Illegal Attempt To Dox Twitter Users!
column52: Amber Heard has been an abusive bully for far too long. She's been able to get away with her crimes. This time she has come after Twitter users, trampling on their 1st Amendment Rights. We want her criminally charged for her legal attepts through her lawyer & the court to invade innocent people's privacy. Amber Heard is a celebrity. She made the choice to pubilcally broadcast her personal drama for the world when she went on various interviews to defame, slander and create her hoax against Johnny Depp. She invited the world into her life. Then she began taking large sums of money to speak on the subject. Amber Heard reacted in fury when her plan backfired & her lies were & still are being exposed. As a result she wishes to control how people discuss the drama she started. I'm asking that Twitter protect out privacy. Otherwise no one will trust the social media site. We want our rights upheld. Please criminally charge Amber Heard for Harassment & Violating our Rights!

column2: Someone has to raise some voices to stop Amber Heard. She thinks her long history of harming people will continue. This harmful pattern of behavior needs an intervention. It seems her family is either like her or afraid of her. (I take all this information from written statements from family & friends of Ambers) People need to be protected from her reign of abuse.

column52: Amber Heard has been an abusive bully for far too long. She's been able to get away with her crimes. This time she has come after Twitter users, trampling on their 1st Amendment Rights. We want her criminally charged for her legal attepts through her lawyer & the court to invade innocent people's privacy. Amber Heard is a celebrity. She made the choice to pubilcally broadcast her personal drama for the world when she went on various interviews to defame, slander and create her hoax against Johnny Depp. She invited the world into her life. Then she began taking large sums of money to speak on the subject. Amber Heard reacted in fury when her plan backfired & her lies were & still are being exposed. As a result she wishes to control how people discuss the drama she started. I'm asking that Twitter protect out privacy. Otherwise no one will trust the social media site. We want our rights upheld. Please criminally charge Amber Heard for Harassment & Violating our Rights!
